        "description": "When I bought the Oculus Quest, about a year after its release, my first goal was to create a game I would be proud of.\n\nWhile digging into my memories, I remembered that I used to spend hours challenging a great classic from my childhood: MicroVision's Brick Breaker.\n\nSince the original version in 1976, many variants have emerged. But I hope you'll enjoy mine, Retro Bricks 1982, both retro & modern.\n\nThe beta version here contains 15 test levels, some music and hopefully a lot of fun!\n\nI wish to be able to offer the final version in the next few weeks. In the meantime, don't hesitate to send me your feedback!\n\nNeoPunk",
